When a custom page template is used, user always have to go through a page template wizard. This is confusing, as the wizard looks exactly the same as the next page, even if only one variable is available. 
It should be possible to disable the template, so that the variables can't be manually manipulated. If this is not an option, then at least make the page wizard only show the fields which are editable.

